Description: A profile to be used in examples, in accordance with [RFC6963].

Common Name: Dublin Core HTML meta data profile
Description:
A set of conventions by which a Dublin Core metadata
        description set can be can be represented within an (X)HTML Web
        page using (X)HTML elements and attributes.

A profile URI to request or signal expanded JSON-LD
        document form.

A profile URI to request or signal compacted JSON-LD
        document form.

A profile URI to request or signal flattened JSON-LD
        document form.
A profile URI to request or signal the document is in the Web Annotation JSON format.
Profile of flattened JSON-LD that follow Research Object RO-Crate specifications.
